Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.21,0:23:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}啊  我也想站上去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.24,0:23:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs40}好啊  等到结束之后吧
